Alhaji Adisa Logun, the Chief of Staff to the Kwara State Governor, is dead. This was confirmed in a twitter post by the Special Assistant, New Media to Kwara State Governor, Fafoluyi Olayinka. He was aged 73. He said, “Kwara State Chief Of Staff, Aminu Adisa Logun Is Dead.. Indeed, death is the next thing after birth. Black Tuesday here in Kwara.” The late Aminu Adisa logun was appointed the Chief of Staff of kwara State Governor in 2019, few weeks after swearing-in of Gov. Abdulrahman Abdulrazaq. Details shortly…